---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Sportiva Gym · Gimnasio solo para damas en Progreso, Yucatán"
  description="Gimnasio exclusivo para mujeres en el Centro de Progreso: súper equipado, cómodo y con instructoras de primera. ⭐ 4.4 con 38 reseñas en Google."
  slug="sportiva-gym"
  ogImage="/sportiva-gym/img/foto_1.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Yeseva+One&family=Karla:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
  favicon="🌸"
  themeColor="#9d174d"
  whatsapp={null}
  telefono={null}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="sg">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <div class="hero-media">
          <img src="/sportiva-gym/img/foto_1.jpg" alt="Área de pesas y máquinas de Sportiva Gym, con el letrero del gimnasio sobre la pared de ladrillo" />
          <div class="hero-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="seal" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="128" height="128">
            <defs>
              <path id="sealRing" d="M 100,100 m -78,0 a 78,78 0 1,1 156,0 a 78,78 0 1,1 -156,0" />
            </defs>
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="94" class="seal-edge" />
            <text class="seal-text">
              <textPath href="#sealRing" startOffset="0%">ESPACIO EXCLUSIVO · PARA MUJERES · SPORTIVA GYM · </textPath>
            </text>
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="44" class="seal-center" />
          </svg>
          <span class="seal-mono" aria-hidden="true">S</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-panel">
        <p class="kicker reveal">Gimnasio · Solo para damas · Centro, Progreso</p>
        <h1 class="poster reveal">Sportiva<br />Gym</h1>
        <p class="tagline reveal">El gimnasio <strong>solo para damas</strong> del Centro de Progreso: cómodo, súper equipado y con instructoras de primera.</p>

        <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.4 · 38 reseñas en Google
        </a>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ NOSOTRAS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="nosotras">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">❀ Nosotras</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Un espacio pensado <span class="berry">solo</span> para ti</h2>
        <div class="about reveal">
          <p>Somos <strong>Sportiva Gym</strong>, un gimnasio en el Centro de Progreso pensado exclusivamente para mujeres. Aquí no compartes máquina, espacio ni ritmo con nadie más: entrenas rodeada de otras mujeres, con la tranquilidad de un lugar hecho para ti.</p>
          <p>Nuestras clientas lo describen mejor que nosotras: <em>«…super equipado y con instructores de primera»</em>, <em>«…excelente trato,buen ambiente e higiene»</em>. Cuidamos cada rincón del gym —de las máquinas a los vestidores— para que cada sesión se sienta cómoda, segura y limpia.</p>
          <p>Si buscas un lugar solo para damas donde entrenar en serio, sin incomodidades ni miradas, te esperamos en la calle 35 del Centro de Progreso.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ INSTALACIONES ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">❀ Qué ofrecemos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Todo lo que necesitas, en un solo lugar</h2>
        <ul class="ofrece reveal">
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Circuito de pesas y máquinas</h3><p>Equipo completo para trabajar todo el cuerpo, a tu ritmo.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Zona de cardio</h3><p>Caminadoras y bicicletas listas para tu rutina aeróbica.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Instructoras de primer nivel</h3><p>Acompañamiento cercano en cada sesión, como cuentan nuestras clientas.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Vestidores y casilleros</h3><p>Llega, cámbiate y guarda tus cosas con toda comodidad.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Ambiente limpio e higiénico</h3><p>Un cuidado que se nota desde que entras por la puerta.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="flor" aria-hidden="true">✿</span>
            <div><h3>Espacio 100% para mujeres</h3><p>Pensado para que entrenes con total confianza, sin excepción.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ RESEÑAS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">❀ Lo que dicen ellas</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal"><span class="berry">4.4 de 5</span> en 38 reseñas</h2>
        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-mark" aria-hidden="true">&#8220;</p>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>Magnífico gimnasio para damas. Super recomendado,  muy cómodo, super equipado y con instructores de primera</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Vanessa Valladares</strong><span>Hace un año · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-mark" aria-hidden="true">&#8220;</p>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>El mejor gym,solo para damas,excelente trato,buen ambiente e higiene.</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Flori Posa</strong><span>Hace 3 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-mark" aria-hidden="true">&#8220;</p>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>Buen lugar y agradable ambiente 😊</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>isabel chan</strong><span>Hace 8 años · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOTOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="galeria">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">❀ Así se ve por dentro</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Nuestro gym, tal cual es</h2>
        <div class="galeria reveal">
          <img src="/sportiva-gym/img/foto_3.jpg" alt="Zona de cardio de Sportiva Gym con caminadoras y bicicletas" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/sportiva-gym/img/foto_2.jpg" alt="Área de pesas de Sportiva Gym" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/sportiva-gym/img/foto_4.jpg" alt="Recepción y vestidores con casilleros de Sportiva Gym" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">❀ Dónde estamos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Centro de Progreso</h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">C. 35 172, Centro<br />97320 Progreso, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>7:30–15:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Sportiva%20Gym%2C%20C.%2035%20172%2C%20Centro%2C%2097320%20Progreso%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: Sportiva Gym en Progreso, Yucatán"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">Ven a conocer tu espacio</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Un gimnasio pensado solo para ti, en el Centro de Progreso.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cómo llegar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo">Sportiva Gym</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Gimnasio solo para damas · C. 35 172, Centro, 97320 Progreso, Yucatán</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=18261731686524890737&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ver en Google Maps</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 6:00–22:00 · Sábado 7:30–15:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "Sportiva Gym",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/sportiva-gym",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "C. 35 172, Centro",
      "addressLocality": "Progreso",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97320",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.4",
      "reviewCount": "38"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 06:00-22:00", "Sa 07:30-15:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --blush: #fdf2f5;
      --cream: #fffaf9;
      --berry: #9d174d;
      --berry-deep: #6f0f39;
      --nude: #e8b4b8;
      --ink: #2a1a22;
      --muted: #8a6c73;
      --line: rgba(42, 26, 34, 0.12);
      --display: "Yeseva One", "Georgia", serif;
      --body: "Karla", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--blush);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .sg ::selection { background: var(--berry); color: var(--blush); }
    .sg a:focus-visible,
    .sg .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--berry);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero-photo {
      position: relative;
      height: 62vh;
      min-height: 340px;
    }
    .hero-media {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-media img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 30%;
    }
    .hero-scrim {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(42, 17, 28, 0.15) 0%, rgba(111, 15, 57, 0.55) 70%, var(--blush) 100%);
    }

    .seal {
      position: absolute;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: -44px;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 128px;
      height: 128px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 22px rgba(42, 17, 28, 0.35));
    }
    .seal svg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      animation: girar 26s linear infinite;
      transform-origin: 50% 50%;
    }
    .seal-edge { fill: var(--cream); stroke: var(--berry); stroke-width: 2; }
    .seal-text {
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      fill: var(--berry-deep);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .seal-center { fill: var(--berry); }
    .seal-mono {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 34px;
      color: var(--blush);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    @keyframes girar { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .hero-panel {
      position: relative;
      padding: 64px 0 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .kicker {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--berry);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .poster {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 0.98;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 15vw, 92px);
      color: var(--berry-deep);
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(17px, 4.4vw, 21px);
      max-width: 34ch;
      margin: 0 auto 22px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .tagline strong { color: var(--berry); font-weight: 700; }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--nude);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: var(--cream);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--berry); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--berry); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; margin: 26px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--berry); color: var(--cream); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: var(--berry-deep); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--berry); color: var(--berry-deep); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--berry); color: var(--cream); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 15px; padding: 12px 20px; }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 70px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--cream); }
    .sec-kicker {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--berry);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 8vw, 54px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin: 0 0 26px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
    }
    .sec-title .berry { color: var(--berry); }

    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: #4a3038; }
    .about strong { color: var(--berry-deep); }
    .about em { color: var(--berry-deep); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }

    /* ---------- OFRECEMOS ---------- */
    .ofrece {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .ofrece li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .ofrece li:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .flor {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: var(--berry);
      line-height: 1.3;
      min-width: 28px;
    }
    .ofrece h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 21px;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
    }
    .ofrece p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15.5px; }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--berry);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 22px 22px 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .rev-mark {
      position: absolute;
      top: 6px;
      right: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 46px;
      color: var(--nude);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .rev-stars { color: var(--berry); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.16em; margin: 0 0 10px; }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 16.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .rev figcaption {
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- GALERÍA ---------- */
    .galeria {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .galeria img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--berry-deep); }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15.5px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--cream); background: var(--berry); font-weight: 700; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--berry-deep);
      color: var(--cream);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      background: var(--berry);
      color: var(--cream);
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 12% 20%, rgba(253, 242, 245, 0.12) 0, transparent 40%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 78%, rgba(253, 242, 245, 0.1) 0, transparent 44%);
    }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7.5vw, 48px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 40ch; font-weight: 500; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--cream); color: var(--berry-deep); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--nude); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--blush);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: var(--berry-deep);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--berry-deep); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--berry); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--berry); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12.5px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .hero-photo { height: 74vh; }
      .hero-panel { padding: 84px 0 56px; }
      .sec { padding: 100px 0; }
      .ofrece { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; column-gap: 48px; }
      .ofrece li:nth-child(2) { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .ofrece li:nth-last-child(2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); align-items: start; }
      .galeria { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 400px; }
      .seal { width: 150px; height: 150px; right: 32px; bottom: -54px; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
